reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Favorite sweaters thicker shirt
reviews.reviewText: This shirt is nice and thick and fits like a shirt but feels like a cozy sweater. The material is so soft and the inside is even more soft and warm. Is great for the cold weather I hit when on vacation in Europe. The oatmeal type color is so flattering and I wear this shirt often and it still looks brand new! Highly recommend!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Stunned by the quality
reviews.reviewText: I, like many other people leaving reviews, was very pleasantly surprised by the quality of this turtleneck! It surprisingly soft and well made given the price point and looks like it cost FAR more than it actually does. I've worn it once thus far and gotten quite a few compliments!It isn't sheer at all and IMO runs true to size. It's a great staple piece to have in a closet and goes well with jeans or slacks. Overall, I have no complaints, very pleasantly surprised. I usually don't trust clothing from amazon but after this, I think I'll be giving some more clothing from this brand a try :) wish it came in more colors honestly.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I am 5 foot 8 inches and this long sleeve fits me perfectly. As a tall girl it is hard to find tshirts that will fit the length and the width of my arms. This turtle neck does just that, it has a good amount of stretch and is super soft and keeps me warm during the mountain winters. However, I will say the turtle neck aspect fits a little looser than I would like it to, but it is still cute and serves its purpose of keeping my neck warm.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 22, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I’m not much for a turtleneck person, I don’t really like them. I was also skeptical because this fabric looked thin and didn’t seem like it would fit nicely. But I actually REALLY like this sweater! The reviews were right, the inside has warm soft material, and it definitely keeps you warm outside! I wore it to a job interview. It compliments the body as well, and it would look cute paired with so many things (the dress I have in one pic was a little too big but I was out of time to exchange it before the interview lmao). Even just with leggings it looks really nice. The outside material is really soft too, and it’s not that trashy type of fabric that collects fuzzies when you dry it. This is a win in my book. 👍🏻 Definitely recommend. Great for price, good, stretchy, soft material. For anyone else who doesn’t care for turtlenecks but looking for one, I recommend this!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Not for me, but nice quality.
reviews.reviewText: The material of this shirt is super super soft, and stretches nicely. It’s also very thick material. It dose fit a little looser than expected, but its so slight that going a size down might be too small. Personally it’s not for me, the material is just too dense and heavy for my liking, but it’s very nice quality and well made.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars So soft, size down,
reviews.reviewText: I am 5’2 about 135lbs and a size 36 DD. I ordered the nude size small and it’s the most soft long sleeve ever. Very warm but not too warm. I run hot and this shirt was ok for a cool day. Not see through which I love. Feels and looks like nice quality, it’s thicker than your basic long sleeve from somewhere like target/old navy. Nice stretch that maintains shape! I wish this shirt was made without a turtle neck because I would buy every color. (My account is under my husbands name! Yes, a women posted this lol)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 11, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Looks exactly like the picture
reviews.reviewText: I am so happy that this top matched the top in the picture! The weight of the package already told me that it’s going to be nice. I loved the feel of the material, very soft and the texture and fit are perfect. The arms have a nice length and covers the wrist nicely. The length is perfect , it sits below the waist so you can tuck it or keep it out. It’s not see through and the chest fits nicely too. I ordered a medium size and I’m so glad because it’s a roomier size. But it still looks like a form fitting top. I haven’t worn it yet so I don’t know if it’s a hot top but it feels like it’s a normal temp when it’s on. Really nice material and I would definitely recommend and order more in the future!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I ordered this turtle neck at the last minute to complete my outfit.. it was supposed to arrive at 7am, then 6pm. Itfinally artived at 7:50 pm as I was walking out the door for the party.. I was surpised by the quality og the material and fit of the shirt. The shirt was soft, smooth, well insulated.. It was just super comfy and slimming. I plan tobuy more

reviews.reviewTitle: Trendy Queen Womens Mock Turtleneck Long Sleeve Shirts Fall Fashion Basic Layering Slim Fit -Large
reviews.reviewText: This item does not fit properly, it's fits like a small when I ordered a large. If you order this product, pick 2 sizes up as the size chart is totally off, as for what it is made, the label says 100% polyester, so you would think it wouldn't shrink.I do not recommend this product at all it's not worth the money.
This product is absolutely NOT true to size. I ordered a Large, and it fits like a Small. For accurate sizing, size down about 2 sizes!! I will be returning.
the sizing is sooo off!! This Large doesn’t even fit me and I wear all Medium and Large for clothes. This doesn’t let my head go through the neck hole
